name: A Very Retro Christmas Note Set
description:
A lovely notecard set.. You will receive 10 notecards and 10 envelopes in your choice of kraft brown or olive green. Perfect for saying hello to an old friend!

Each notecard measures 5 x 7 inches with ample space for writing a quick note to a friend. Inside is blank.

Cards are printed on thick eco friendly 130lb matte finish cover stock. And everything is professionally printed to ensure quality and color-richness.

Comes packaged nicely for keeping or gift-giving.

Larger quantities are available upon request.
